Notes: Array of 0-5 photos showing other vehicles, property damage, or documents - Optional field
1st uploaded image - Maps to file_url_other_vehicle column in incident_other_vehicles table
2nd uploaded image - Maps to file_url_other_vehicle_1 column in incident_other_vehicles table
3rd uploaded image - Stored only in user_documents (no incident_other_vehicles mapping)
4th uploaded image - Stored only in user_documents (no incident_other_vehicles mapping)
5th uploaded image - Stored only in user_documents (no incident_other_vehicles mapping)
Temp session ID for upload tracking - Reused from previous pages (Page 6 creates it), shared across all photo uploads
JavaScript array of image objects stored in localStorage - Contains: path, fileName, fileSize, fieldName, blobUrl
Temporary storage path for each uploaded image - Moved to permanent storage on form submission
Original filename of uploaded image - Stored in localStorage for display purposes
Formatted file size (e.g., '2.3 MB') - Stored in localStorage for display purposes
Dynamic field name assigned per slot (other_vehicle_photo_1/2 or other_damage_photo_3/4/5) - Stored in user_documents
Temporary blob URL for preview display - Created via URL.createObjectURL(), revoked on removal, not persisted
